description:
Author : @Kiri Karma
Divers 2022 - Helltopia Brussels Halloweex

The Helltopia mott breaks out of its slimy cocoon after a long break.

Helltopia is back in 2022 and just like the monsters it proudly brings to life, our Horror concept is also transforming form. This year not as a festival but as an underground expo in Brussels.

It is a true Horror festival with film screenings, lectures, podcasts, but as the main theme an exhibition entirely devoted to Pop Culture around Horror.

Brussels Halloweex: 13 Days Of Horror.

Come visit us from October 21 to November 666 if you dare!

Van Gogh in America
Self-Portait, 1887
On the evening of January 31, 1922, the Detroit Institute of Arts made history when it became the first public museum the United States to purchase a Van Gogh, this painting.

Van Gogh in America
Grapes, Lemons, Pears, and Apples, 1887
Van Gogh's technique changed significantly after he moved to Paris and began to incorporate vibrant colors and stippled Pointillist brushwork in his paintings. He produced more than 170 still-life paintings over his career as they allowed him to experiment with color and brushwork.

description: Eastgate House, Rochester, 27 October 2022. Built in the 1590-91 for Sir Peter Buck, Clerk of the Acts of the Navy Board, Clerk of the Cheque at Chatham Royal Naval Dockyard, and Mayor of Medway. It is now a Dicken's Museum as it features in Charles Dicken's 'Pickwick Papers' as 'Westgate' and in 'The Mystery of Edwin Drood' as 'The Nun's House'. He was writing the latter novel in the Swiss Chalet, Gadd's Hill (now relocated to the garden of Eastgate House) when he died. Pictured is the Swiss Chalet between Eastgate House (left) and the Charles Dickens Centre(right).

description: Cotinus coggygria 'Royal Purple' WW44 Smoke Tree N4- (SmokeBush) Smoke Tree, Mature plant size: 15x12ft., PURPLE, purple leaves, yellow flowers, USDA Hardiness Zone 4, Michigan Bloom Month -, In Garden Bed N4 for 12 MONTHS (Lowes,). Planted in 2021. Missouri Botanical Garden: ‘Royal Purple’ is a compact, purple-leaved version of the European species. It is a deciduous, upright, loose-spreading, multi-stemmed shrub that typically matures over time to 10-15' tall. As is the case with all plants of this species, it gets its common name of smoketree (or smokebush) not from the tiny, insignificant, yellowish flowers which appear in branching, terminal panicles (6-8” long) in spring, but from the billowy hairs (attached to elongated stalks on the spent flower clusters) which turn a smoky pink to purplish pink in late spring, thus covering the plant with fluffy, hazy, smoke-like puffs throughout summer. But it is the foliage that particularly distinguishes 'Royal Purple'. Ovate to obovate leaves (to 3” long) emerge a rich maroon red in spring, and then gradually mature to dark purplish-red to purplish-black in summer. Foliage retains good color without much fading throughout the growing season. Cotinus is in the same family as and closely related to the sumacs (Rhus). 'Royal Purple' was raised at Lombarts Nursery in Boskoop, Holland. It was introduced into the U.S. in 1953. Synonymous with C. coggygria 'Kromhout'. 2021 note: slected plant with single trunk, will try to keep it that way. Photo by F.D.Richards, SE Michigan. description: Inmo Divers

El presidente de la Junta de Andalucía, Juanma Moreno, se ha reunido
esta mañana en el Palacio de San Telmo con los promotores del Proyecto
Carnaval de Cádiz, Patrimonio Inmaterial de la Humanidad, entre los que
se encuentra el Rector Magnífico de la Universidad de Cádiz, Francisco
Pinella, y el director de la Cátedra del Carnaval de la UCA, Alberto Ramos.

Colocar al Carnaval en el escaparate internacional con rango de

description: Van Gogh in America

Van Gogh in America
Le Moulin de la Galette, 1886
This painting shows the Moulin de la Galette, one of the three remaining windmills (moulins) on the Montmartre, the large hill located in the northern section of Paris where Van Gogh moved in 1886. The Moulin de la Galette, part of a complex that included gardens, a dance hall, and cafes, was located a few blocks from the apartment Van Gogh shared with his brother Theo.

description:
El presidente de la Junta de Andalucía, Juanma Moreno, ha indicado hoy que Andalucía tiene
que tratar y abordar el problema del agua y de la sequía con a corto, medio y largo plazo, ya
que esta tierra necesita que sus políticas de agua, que son fundamentales para su progreso
y desarrollo económico, estén siempre y en todo momento en el centro de la acción política,
al mismo tiempo que ha insistido en la importancia de actuar siempre con planificación,
previsión y orden. “El Gobierno andaluz tiene una hoja de ruta clara en materia hídrica”.
Moreno ha presidido en el Palacio de San Telmo la reunión del Comité de Expertos de la
Sequía que se enmarca dentro del Plan SOS que el Gobierno andaluz ha puesto en marcha
para impulsar medidas e inversiones por valor de algo más de 4.000 millones de euros hasta
2027 y que complementará a la Comisión de Seguimiento por la Sequía, creada en pasado
mes de septiembre.
En este sentido, ha aseverado que esta comunidad cuenta ya con dos órganos de excepción
en materia de asesoramiento para abordar de forma estructural, planificada e integral un plan
que permita optimizar cada gota de agua, ganar en eficiencia e innovar en soluciones para
aprovechar al máximo el agua que es desarrollo y progreso para hoy y para las generaciones
futuras.
Este Comité está compuesto por diez expertos seleccionados por la Consejería de Agricultura,
Agua y Desarrollo Rural en base a sus perfiles profesionales, trayectorias y especialidades y
que aúnan lo mejor en torno a las políticas de agua, por lo que arrojarán la luz necesaria para
abordar este asunto como Andalucía merece.
De este modo, ha incidido en que, con sus apreciaciones, el Ejecutivo andaluz podrá valorar
la situación en cada momento, priorizar objetivos y trazar actuaciones a todos los niveles, al
mismo tiempo que ha explicado que del agua dependen dos pilares claves en la economía
andaluza como es la agroindustria y el turismo, sectores de los que también dependen miles
y miles de empleos y de familia.


En este punto, ha manifestado que este Comité de Expertos ayudará a saber qué es lo que
se debe hacer de cara al futuro para poder acertar en las inversiones y en las decisiones y
garantizar así el suministro a todos los sectores.
A este respecto, ha incidido en que el Gobierno andaluz trabaja para buscar fórmulas y para
analizar la situación con rigor y con seriedad, abstrayéndose de los debates políticos,
compartiendo información y buscando y compartiendo propuestas sensatas y certeras.
Finalmente, ha pedido a los andaluces que sean sensibles con la gestión que hacen del agua
y que sean también prudentes y responsables con su consumo porque, según ha dicho, es
un bien escaso que hay que preservar y apreciar. “Pido a la sociedad un esfuerzo a partir de
ya para gestionar y consumir el agua de manera responsable”, ha concluido.

consejero de Presidencia, Interior, Diálogo Social y Simplificación Administrativa, Antonio
Sanz; la consejera de Agricultura, Pesca, Agua y Desarrollo Rural, Carmen Crespo; y el

description:
Author : @Kiri Karma
Divers 2022 - Helltopia Brussels Halloweex

The Helltopia mott breaks out of its slimy cocoon after a long break.

Helltopia is back in 2022 and just like the monsters it proudly brings to life, our Horror concept is also transforming form. This year not as a festival but as an underground expo in Brussels.

It is a true Horror festival with film screenings, lectures, podcasts, but as the main theme an exhibition entirely devoted to Pop Culture around Horror.

Brussels Halloweex: 13 Days Of Horror.

Come visit us from October 21 to November 666 if you dare!

description:
Divers 2022 - Helltopia Brussels Halloweex

The Helltopia mott breaks out of its slimy cocoon after a long break.

Helltopia is back in 2022 and just like the monsters it proudly brings to life, our Horror concept is also transforming form. This year not as a festival but as an underground expo in Brussels.

It is a true Horror festival with film screenings, lectures, podcasts, but as the main theme an exhibition entirely devoted to Pop Culture around Horror.

Brussels Halloweex: 13 Days Of Horror.

Come visit us from October 21 to November 666 if you dare!

description: Eastgate House, Rochester, 27 October 2022. Built in the 1590-91 for Sir Peter Buck, Clerk of the Acts of the Navy Board, Clerk of the Cheque at Chatham Royal Naval Dockyard, and Mayor of Medway. It is now a Dicken's Museum as it features in Charles Dicken's 'Pickwick Papers' as 'Westgate' and in 'The Mystery of Edwin Drood' as 'The Nun's House'. He was writing the latter novel in the Swiss Chalet, Gadd's Hill (now relocated to the garden of Eastgate House) when he died. Pictured is some wall decoration.

description:
El presidente de la Junta de Andalucía, Juanma Moreno, se ha reunido
esta mañana en el Palacio de San Telmo con los promotores del Proyecto
Carnaval de Cádiz, Patrimonio Inmaterial de la Humanidad, entre los que
se encuentra el Rector Magnífico de la Universidad de Cádiz, Francisco
Pinella, y el director de la Cátedra del Carnaval de la UCA, Alberto Ramos.

Colocar al Carnaval en el escaparate internacional con rango de
Patrimonio Inmaterial de la Humanidad, supondría un impulso
importantísimo a la ciudad y a la provincia a todos los niveles, con el
consiguiente impacto económico. Esta candidatura supone consolidar a
nivel mundial un acontecimiento cultural y social de siglos e implica un
enorme movimiento vecinal articulado a través de cientos de peñas y
agrupaciones, así como la participación en esta fiesta de propios y
visitantes. Además, genera una producción artística de primer rango y
afecta de forma positiva a muy diversos ámbitos, desde la gastronomía
hasta el transporte y también a la imagen de Cádiz.

En la reunión también han estado presentes el consejero de Presidencia,
Interior, Diálogo Social y Simplificación Administrativa, Antonio Sanz,
y el consejero de Turismo, Cultura y Deporte, Arturo Bernal.


————-


Fotografía oficial de la Junta de Andalucía, se pone a disposición solamente para su publicación por las organizaciones de noticias y/o para la impresión de uso personal por parte del sujeto (s) de la fotografía. La fotografía no puede ser manipulada de ninguna manera y no se puede utilizar en materiales comerciales o políticos, los anuncios, productos, promociones que de alguna manera sugieran aprobación o respaldo de la Junta de Andalucía.

Author : @Kiri Karma
Divers 2022 - Helltopia Brussels Halloweex

The Helltopia mott breaks out of its slimy cocoon after a long break.

Helltopia is back in 2022 and just like the monsters it proudly brings to life, our Horror concept is also transforming form. This year not as a festival but as an underground expo in Brussels.

It is a true Horror festival with film screenings, lectures, podcasts, but as the main theme an exhibition entirely devoted to Pop Culture around Horror.

Brussels Halloweex: 13 Days Of Horror.

Come visit us from October 21 to November 666 if you dare!

Divers 2022 - Helltopia Brussels Halloweex

The Helltopia mott breaks out of its slimy cocoon after a long break.

Helltopia is back in 2022 and just like the monsters it proudly brings to life, our Horror concept is also transforming form. This year not as a festival but as an underground expo in Brussels.

It is a true Horror festival with film screenings, lectures, podcasts, but as the main theme an exhibition entirely devoted to Pop Culture around Horror.

Brussels Halloweex: 13 Days Of Horror.

Come visit us from October 21 to November 666 if you dare!

description:
03 de Noviembre de 2022.- Encuentro Federal de Gestión Cultural Pública

Foto: Soledad Amarilla / Ministerio de Cultura de la Nación

Chionanthus retusus WW44 Chinese Fringe Tree N4- (Chinese Fringetree) Chinese Fringe Tree, Mature plant size: 15-25ft., white, USDA Hardiness Zone 5, Michigan Bloom Month -, In Garden Bed N4 for 3.5 YEARS (Dog). Planted in 2019. Missouri Botanical Garden: Chionanthus retusus, commonly called Chinese fringetree, is native to China, Korea and Japan. As with the native U.S. species (C. virginicus), this plant is noted for its profuse spring bloom of fragrant white flowers. It is most often seen in cultivation as a large, multi-stemmed, deciduous shrub growing to 10-20’ tall with a rounded, wide-spreading form. It also may be grown as a small tree (multi-trunked or trained as a single trunk), ultimately reaching up to 30-40’ tall. Terminal clusters (to 4” long) of mildly fragrant, pure white flowers with fringe-like petals bloom in late spring to early summer. Bloom appears about 2-3 weeks before that of C. virginicus. Plants are primarily dioecious (separate male and female plants), but some plants may have some perfect flowers. Male flowers are slightly showier. Female flowers (if fertilized) give way to clusters of olive-like fruits (each to 1/2”long) which ripen to a dark bluish black in late summer/fall and are a good food source for birds and wildlife. Lustrous, leathery leaves are ovate to elliptic and 4” long. Leaves on young plants have serrate margins. Leaves are bright green above and whitish-green plus downy beneath. Leaves turn yellow in fall (reportedly more attractive in northern areas). Exfoliating gray-brown bark is attractive in winter. Genus name comes from the Greek words chion meaning snow and anthos meaning a flower for the snow white flowers of C. virginicus. Specific epithet means rounded with a shallow notch at the apex, in reference to leaf shape. Large shrub that can be grown as a small tree. Gray bark may be peeling or tightly ridged. Leaves leathery & lustrous. Just as beautiful as the Virginia Fringe Tree and with the advantage that it will take limey as well as acid soil. Looks like a dome of snow. MSU Karen Gentry Suggestion. AHS 75 Great American Garden Plants. Photo by F.D.Richards, SE Michigan. Link to additional photos of this plant from 2019, 20, 21, 22: www.flickr.com/search/?user_id=50697352%40N00&sort=da... #Michigan, #49236, #usdaZone6, #Tree, #Chionanthus, #ChineseFringeTree, #WW44

description:
Author : @Kiri Karma
BCWF Wrestling - La Rentree Des Clashs 2022 - Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Vs Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Def. (Pin) Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Info on the match : Avant de commencer le match, le GM avait encore plus de ' Encore une chose ' dans sa manche. Non seulement il a autorise l'annonceur Rocky Jones dans le match, mais dans une grande surprise, il a egalement presente le monstre hollandais, Ymah Pain !
Voordat de wedstrijd begon, had de GM nog wat 'One more things' in petto. Niet alleen liet hij omroeper Rocky Jones toe in de wedstrijd, maar als grote verrassing introduceerde hij ook het monster uit Nederland, Ymah Pain!
Before starting the match, the GM had some more 'One more things' up his sleeve. Not only did he allow announcer Rocky Jones into the match, but in a big surprise he introduced the monster from Holland, Ymah Pain, as well!

Avec toutes les chances contre eux, Eddie et Tibo ont demande a Joey de reintegrer Mama, s'ils remportaient la victoire improbable. Joey a accepte, mais son rire s'est vite transforme en panique quand Eddie a sorti son troisieme partenaire pour le match, LEGION !
Met hun rug tegen de muur, vroegen Eddie en Tibo Joey om Mama weer aan te nemen, mochten ze de onwaarschijnlijke overwinning behalen. Joey stemde toe, maar zijn lach sloeg al snel om in paniek toen Eddie zijn derde partner voor de wedstrijd tevoorschijn haalde, LEGION!
With the odds stacked against them, Eddie and Tibo asked Joey to reinstate Mama, should they pick up the unlikely win. Joey agreed, but his laughter soon turned to panic as Eddie brought out his third partner for the match, LEGION!

A la fin, Eddie a reussi a remporter la victoire inattendue sur Mayeck. Il a termine la soiree en annoncant que Mama serait de retour au prochain spectacle !
Na een heen en weer wedstrijd wist Eddie dan toch de overwinning te pakken door Mayeck te pinnen. Hij eindigde de avond door aan te kondigen dat Mama terug zou keren bij de volgende show!
After a back-and forth match, Eddie managed to pick up the upset win by pinning Mayeck. He ended the night by announcing Mama would be back at the next show!

 ( Il sera bientot temps de retourner a l'ecole ! Mais cela ne signifie pas que vous ne pouvez pas passer un bon moment chez nous. Venez rejoindre le BWS le 2 septembre a Grivegnee pour une nuit de catch ! Retournons a l'ecole en beaute. )

description:
During a series of observing runs at one of the the Keck 10m telescopes on Mauna Kea in Hawaii, I was allowed into the mirror laboratory where the hexagonal mirror segments were cleaned and re-coated.

Using a Hasselblad with the 30mm FishEye lens in 1997, I was able to photograph segments at different stages of the process. This image catches me reflected in the corner of one of them with its fresh aluminium coat.

Working with Marshall Cohen (Caltech) and in collaboration with Sperello di Serego Alighieri (ST-ECF/ESO), Andrea Cimatti (ESO) and Joel Vernet (ESO), we were using spectro-polarimetry to identify and study the scattered light from the obscured quasars in the nuclei of distant radio galaxies.

This produced a unique set of data showing that regions of gas and dust in the host galaxies acted as a mirror to provide a view of the central supermassive black hole. The reflected light revealed itself by its linear polarisation very much in the same way as a clear blue sky is highly polarised in a way that can easily be demonstrated using a pair of polarising sunglasses.

description:
BCWF Wrestling - La Rentree Des Clashs 2022 - Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Vs Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Def. (Pin) Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Info on the match : Avant de commencer le match, le GM avait encore plus de ' Encore une chose ' dans sa manche. Non seulement il a autorise l'annonceur Rocky Jones dans le match, mais dans une grande surprise, il a egalement presente le monstre hollandais, Ymah Pain !
Voordat de wedstrijd begon, had de GM nog wat 'One more things' in petto. Niet alleen liet hij omroeper Rocky Jones toe in de wedstrijd, maar als grote verrassing introduceerde hij ook het monster uit Nederland, Ymah Pain!
Before starting the match, the GM had some more 'One more things' up his sleeve. Not only did he allow announcer Rocky Jones into the match, but in a big surprise he introduced the monster from Holland, Ymah Pain, as well!

Avec toutes les chances contre eux, Eddie et Tibo ont demande a Joey de reintegrer Mama, s'ils remportaient la victoire improbable. Joey a accepte, mais son rire s'est vite transforme en panique quand Eddie a sorti son troisieme partenaire pour le match, LEGION !
Met hun rug tegen de muur, vroegen Eddie en Tibo Joey om Mama weer aan te nemen, mochten ze de onwaarschijnlijke overwinning behalen. Joey stemde toe, maar zijn lach sloeg al snel om in paniek toen Eddie zijn derde partner voor de wedstrijd tevoorschijn haalde, LEGION!
With the odds stacked against them, Eddie and Tibo asked Joey to reinstate Mama, should they pick up the unlikely win. Joey agreed, but his laughter soon turned to panic as Eddie brought out his third partner for the match, LEGION!

A la fin, Eddie a reussi a remporter la victoire inattendue sur Mayeck. Il a termine la soiree en annoncant que Mama serait de retour au prochain spectacle !
Na een heen en weer wedstrijd wist Eddie dan toch de overwinning te pakken door Mayeck te pinnen. Hij eindigde de avond door aan te kondigen dat Mama terug zou keren bij de volgende show!
After a back-and forth match, Eddie managed to pick up the upset win by pinning Mayeck. He ended the night by announcing Mama would be back at the next show!

 ( Il sera bientot temps de retourner a l'ecole ! Mais cela ne signifie pas que vous ne pouvez pas passer un bon moment chez nous. Venez rejoindre le BWS le 2 septembre a Grivegnee pour une nuit de catch ! Retournons a l'ecole en beaute. )

BCWF Wrestling - La Rentree Des Clashs 2022 - Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Vs Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Def. (Pin) Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Info on the match : Avant de commencer le match, le GM avait encore plus de ' Encore une chose ' dans sa manche. Non seulement il a autorise l'annonceur Rocky Jones dans le match, mais dans une grande surprise, il a egalement presente le monstre hollandais, Ymah Pain !
Voordat de wedstrijd begon, had de GM nog wat 'One more things' in petto. Niet alleen liet hij omroeper Rocky Jones toe in de wedstrijd, maar als grote verrassing introduceerde hij ook het monster uit Nederland, Ymah Pain!
Before starting the match, the GM had some more 'One more things' up his sleeve. Not only did he allow announcer Rocky Jones into the match, but in a big surprise he introduced the monster from Holland, Ymah Pain, as well!

Avec toutes les chances contre eux, Eddie et Tibo ont demande a Joey de reintegrer Mama, s'ils remportaient la victoire improbable. Joey a accepte, mais son rire s'est vite transforme en panique quand Eddie a sorti son troisieme partenaire pour le match, LEGION !
Met hun rug tegen de muur, vroegen Eddie en Tibo Joey om Mama weer aan te nemen, mochten ze de onwaarschijnlijke overwinning behalen. Joey stemde toe, maar zijn lach sloeg al snel om in paniek toen Eddie zijn derde partner voor de wedstrijd tevoorschijn haalde, LEGION!
With the odds stacked against them, Eddie and Tibo asked Joey to reinstate Mama, should they pick up the unlikely win. Joey agreed, but his laughter soon turned to panic as Eddie brought out his third partner for the match, LEGION!

A la fin, Eddie a reussi a remporter la victoire inattendue sur Mayeck. Il a termine la soiree en annoncant que Mama serait de retour au prochain spectacle !
Na een heen en weer wedstrijd wist Eddie dan toch de overwinning te pakken door Mayeck te pinnen. Hij eindigde de avond door aan te kondigen dat Mama terug zou keren bij de volgende show!
After a back-and forth match, Eddie managed to pick up the upset win by pinning Mayeck. He ended the night by announcing Mama would be back at the next show!

 ( Il sera bientot temps de retourner a l'ecole ! Mais cela ne signifie pas que vous ne pouvez pas passer un bon moment chez nous. Venez rejoindre le BWS le 2 septembre a Grivegnee pour une nuit de catch ! Retournons a l'ecole en beaute. )

description:
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Alison Sudol

Alison Sudol

aka Queenie Goldstein
Fantastic Beasts

Our next guest is an immensely talented actress and musician who came to rise in the Harry Potter prequel franchise Fantastic Beasts and Where To Find Them as the role of the beloved witch Queenie Goldstein opposite co-stars Eddie Redmayne, Jude Law, Ezra Miller and Mads Mikkelsen!

We are of course talking about the amazing Alison Sudol! In the movies she plays Tina Goldstein's younger sister and has the talent of being a very skilled Legilimens (someone who can read minds). She and Jacob Kowalski fall deeply in love, but she falls in the claws of the evil wizard Grindelwald. Currently Alison Sudol is working on a British independent movie called BONUS TRACK.

description:
Author : @Kiri Karma
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Alison Sudol

Alison Sudol

aka Queenie Goldstein
Fantastic Beasts

Our next guest is an immensely talented actress and musician who came to rise in the Harry Potter prequel franchise Fantastic Beasts and Where To Find Them as the role of the beloved witch Queenie Goldstein opposite co-stars Eddie Redmayne, Jude Law, Ezra Miller and Mads Mikkelsen!

We are of course talking about the amazing Alison Sudol! In the movies she plays Tina Goldstein's younger sister and has the talent of being a very skilled Legilimens (someone who can read minds). She and Jacob Kowalski fall deeply in love, but she falls in the claws of the evil wizard Grindelwald. Currently Alison Sudol is working on a British independent movie called BONUS TRACK.

description: Lego 76217 I am Groot

BCWF Wrestling - La Rentree Des Clashs 2022 - Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Vs Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Def. (Pin) Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Info on the match : Avant de commencer le match, le GM avait encore plus de ' Encore une chose ' dans sa manche. Non seulement il a autorise l'annonceur Rocky Jones dans le match, mais dans une grande surprise, il a egalement presente le monstre hollandais, Ymah Pain !
Voordat de wedstrijd begon, had de GM nog wat 'One more things' in petto. Niet alleen liet hij omroeper Rocky Jones toe in de wedstrijd, maar als grote verrassing introduceerde hij ook het monster uit Nederland, Ymah Pain!
Before starting the match, the GM had some more 'One more things' up his sleeve. Not only did he allow announcer Rocky Jones into the match, but in a big surprise he introduced the monster from Holland, Ymah Pain, as well!

Avec toutes les chances contre eux, Eddie et Tibo ont demande a Joey de reintegrer Mama, s'ils remportaient la victoire improbable. Joey a accepte, mais son rire s'est vite transforme en panique quand Eddie a sorti son troisieme partenaire pour le match, LEGION !
Met hun rug tegen de muur, vroegen Eddie en Tibo Joey om Mama weer aan te nemen, mochten ze de onwaarschijnlijke overwinning behalen. Joey stemde toe, maar zijn lach sloeg al snel om in paniek toen Eddie zijn derde partner voor de wedstrijd tevoorschijn haalde, LEGION!
With the odds stacked against them, Eddie and Tibo asked Joey to reinstate Mama, should they pick up the unlikely win. Joey agreed, but his laughter soon turned to panic as Eddie brought out his third partner for the match, LEGION!

A la fin, Eddie a reussi a remporter la victoire inattendue sur Mayeck. Il a termine la soiree en annoncant que Mama serait de retour au prochain spectacle !
Na een heen en weer wedstrijd wist Eddie dan toch de overwinning te pakken door Mayeck te pinnen. Hij eindigde de avond door aan te kondigen dat Mama terug zou keren bij de volgende show!
After a back-and forth match, Eddie managed to pick up the upset win by pinning Mayeck. He ended the night by announcing Mama would be back at the next show!

 ( Il sera bientot temps de retourner a l'ecole ! Mais cela ne signifie pas que vous ne pouvez pas passer un bon moment chez nous. Venez rejoindre le BWS le 2 septembre a Grivegnee pour une nuit de catch ! Retournons a l'ecole en beaute. )

description:
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Alison Sudol

Alison Sudol

aka Queenie Goldstein
Fantastic Beasts

Our next guest is an immensely talented actress and musician who came to rise in the Harry Potter prequel franchise Fantastic Beasts and Where To Find Them as the role of the beloved witch Queenie Goldstein opposite co-stars Eddie Redmayne, Jude Law, Ezra Miller and Mads Mikkelsen!

We are of course talking about the amazing Alison Sudol! In the movies she plays Tina Goldstein's younger sister and has the talent of being a very skilled Legilimens (someone who can read minds). She and Jacob Kowalski fall deeply in love, but she falls in the claws of the evil wizard Grindelwald. Currently Alison Sudol is working on a British independent movie called BONUS TRACK.

Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Alison Sudol

Alison Sudol

aka Queenie Goldstein
Fantastic Beasts

Our next guest is an immensely talented actress and musician who came to rise in the Harry Potter prequel franchise Fantastic Beasts and Where To Find Them as the role of the beloved witch Queenie Goldstein opposite co-stars Eddie Redmayne, Jude Law, Ezra Miller and Mads Mikkelsen!

We are of course talking about the amazing Alison Sudol! In the movies she plays Tina Goldstein's younger sister and has the talent of being a very skilled Legilimens (someone who can read minds). She and Jacob Kowalski fall deeply in love, but she falls in the claws of the evil wizard Grindelwald. Currently Alison Sudol is working on a British independent movie called BONUS TRACK.

전한

플리커 채널 'Republic of Korea'에 게재되는 대한민국정부 사진은 올바른 저작권 이름 (촬영자 / 상기 명기된 기관)으로 표기한 이후 보도 혹은 공익목적으로 사용하실 수 있습니다.

의미를 왜곡하는 맥락에서 사진을 게시하고 재판매, 부분 복제, 변조 또는 다른 이미지에 통합하는 것과 같은 사진의 모든 수정, 자료를 제3자에게 제공하는 것은 대한민국정부(운영자/저작권자)의 명시적인 허가 없이 금지됩니다.

Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Alison Sudol

Alison Sudol

aka Queenie Goldstein
Fantastic Beasts

Our next guest is an immensely talented actress and musician who came to rise in the Harry Potter prequel franchise Fantastic Beasts and Where To Find Them as the role of the beloved witch Queenie Goldstein opposite co-stars Eddie Redmayne, Jude Law, Ezra Miller and Mads Mikkelsen!

We are of course talking about the amazing Alison Sudol! In the movies she plays Tina Goldstein's younger sister and has the talent of being a very skilled Legilimens (someone who can read minds). She and Jacob Kowalski fall deeply in love, but she falls in the claws of the evil wizard Grindelwald. Currently Alison Sudol is working on a British independent movie called BONUS TRACK.

description:
Author : @Kiri Karma
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Alison Sudol

Alison Sudol

aka Queenie Goldstein
Fantastic Beasts

Our next guest is an immensely talented actress and musician who came to rise in the Harry Potter prequel franchise Fantastic Beasts and Where To Find Them as the role of the beloved witch Queenie Goldstein opposite co-stars Eddie Redmayne, Jude Law, Ezra Miller and Mads Mikkelsen!

We are of course talking about the amazing Alison Sudol! In the movies she plays Tina Goldstein's younger sister and has the talent of being a very skilled Legilimens (someone who can read minds). She and Jacob Kowalski fall deeply in love, but she falls in the claws of the evil wizard Grindelwald. Currently Alison Sudol is working on a British independent movie called BONUS TRACK.

description:
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Christopher Lloyd

Christopher Lloyd

aka 'Doc'/dr. Emmett Brown, Uncle Fester, Dr. Doom, Kruge,..
Back To The Future Trilogy - The Addams Family - Who Framed Roger Rabbit - Star Trek - ...

Great Scott!
Our next guest has had such an impact on pop culture that we can speak of a living legend and icon.
Since the 1960s, he has made people smile, laugh and dream.

From a Taxi to a flying Delorean and beyond the boundaries of time and space.

It's a real honor to welcome the most famous time-traveller in the mulitverse and it's his only European show this year!

The one and only Christopher Lloyd is coming to celebrate his 84th birthday at the convention for all the real fans: Comic Con Brussels!

Christopher was in all the Back To The Future movies as 'Doc', Uncle Fester in The Addams Family, Dr. Doom in Who Framed Roger Rabbit, Kruge in Star Trek, Clue and significant roles in 12 Monkeys, Cyberchase, Anastasia, One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest, Piranha 3D and 3DD, The Pagemaster, The Simpsons, Rick and Morty and in the future even in the new season of The Mandalorian..

It's just a great honor to welcome him in Brussels for the first time ever.

description:
BCWF Wrestling - La Rentree Des Clashs 2022 - Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Vs Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Def. (Pin) Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Info on the match : Avant de commencer le match, le GM avait encore plus de ' Encore une chose ' dans sa manche. Non seulement il a autorise l'annonceur Rocky Jones dans le match, mais dans une grande surprise, il a egalement presente le monstre hollandais, Ymah Pain !
Voordat de wedstrijd begon, had de GM nog wat 'One more things' in petto. Niet alleen liet hij omroeper Rocky Jones toe in de wedstrijd, maar als grote verrassing introduceerde hij ook het monster uit Nederland, Ymah Pain!
Before starting the match, the GM had some more 'One more things' up his sleeve. Not only did he allow announcer Rocky Jones into the match, but in a big surprise he introduced the monster from Holland, Ymah Pain, as well!

Avec toutes les chances contre eux, Eddie et Tibo ont demande a Joey de reintegrer Mama, s'ils remportaient la victoire improbable. Joey a accepte, mais son rire s'est vite transforme en panique quand Eddie a sorti son troisieme partenaire pour le match, LEGION !
Met hun rug tegen de muur, vroegen Eddie en Tibo Joey om Mama weer aan te nemen, mochten ze de onwaarschijnlijke overwinning behalen. Joey stemde toe, maar zijn lach sloeg al snel om in paniek toen Eddie zijn derde partner voor de wedstrijd tevoorschijn haalde, LEGION!
With the odds stacked against them, Eddie and Tibo asked Joey to reinstate Mama, should they pick up the unlikely win. Joey agreed, but his laughter soon turned to panic as Eddie brought out his third partner for the match, LEGION!

A la fin, Eddie a reussi a remporter la victoire inattendue sur Mayeck. Il a termine la soiree en annoncant que Mama serait de retour au prochain spectacle !
Na een heen en weer wedstrijd wist Eddie dan toch de overwinning te pakken door Mayeck te pinnen. Hij eindigde de avond door aan te kondigen dat Mama terug zou keren bij de volgende show!
After a back-and forth match, Eddie managed to pick up the upset win by pinning Mayeck. He ended the night by announcing Mama would be back at the next show!

 ( Il sera bientot temps de retourner a l'ecole ! Mais cela ne signifie pas que vous ne pouvez pas passer un bon moment chez nous. Venez rejoindre le BWS le 2 septembre a Grivegnee pour une nuit de catch ! Retournons a l'ecole en beaute. )

description:
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Christopher Lloyd

Christopher Lloyd

aka 'Doc'/dr. Emmett Brown, Uncle Fester, Dr. Doom, Kruge,..
Back To The Future Trilogy - The Addams Family - Who Framed Roger Rabbit - Star Trek - ...

Great Scott!
Our next guest has had such an impact on pop culture that we can speak of a living legend and icon.
Since the 1960s, he has made people smile, laugh and dream.

From a Taxi to a flying Delorean and beyond the boundaries of time and space.

It's a real honor to welcome the most famous time-traveller in the mulitverse and it's his only European show this year!

The one and only Christopher Lloyd is coming to celebrate his 84th birthday at the convention for all the real fans: Comic Con Brussels!

Christopher was in all the Back To The Future movies as 'Doc', Uncle Fester in The Addams Family, Dr. Doom in Who Framed Roger Rabbit, Kruge in Star Trek, Clue and significant roles in 12 Monkeys, Cyberchase, Anastasia, One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest, Piranha 3D and 3DD, The Pagemaster, The Simpsons, Rick and Morty and in the future even in the new season of The Mandalorian..

It's just a great honor to welcome him in Brussels for the first time ever.

 ( Comic con brussels is your celebration of geek culture in the heart of europe!

You will find us at the beautiful Tour & Taxis site near the Brussels North train station. At Comic Con Brussels you will find Dealers, Artists, Actors, ... It's a Con that brings together all the things you love:
Comics, cosplay, gaming, films, manga, collectibles, anime, tv series, clothing, toys, gadgets and lots more!!!

There are still tickets at the register - Cosplay ticket 25 euro & standard ticket 30 euro )

description:
Author : @Kiri Karma
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Christopher Lloyd

Christopher Lloyd

aka 'Doc'/dr. Emmett Brown, Uncle Fester, Dr. Doom, Kruge,..
Back To The Future Trilogy - The Addams Family - Who Framed Roger Rabbit - Star Trek - ...

Great Scott!
Our next guest has had such an impact on pop culture that we can speak of a living legend and icon.
Since the 1960s, he has made people smile, laugh and dream.

From a Taxi to a flying Delorean and beyond the boundaries of time and space.

It's a real honor to welcome the most famous time-traveller in the mulitverse and it's his only European show this year!

The one and only Christopher Lloyd is coming to celebrate his 84th birthday at the convention for all the real fans: Comic Con Brussels!

Christopher was in all the Back To The Future movies as 'Doc', Uncle Fester in The Addams Family, Dr. Doom in Who Framed Roger Rabbit, Kruge in Star Trek, Clue and significant roles in 12 Monkeys, Cyberchase, Anastasia, One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest, Piranha 3D and 3DD, The Pagemaster, The Simpsons, Rick and Morty and in the future even in the new season of The Mandalorian..

It's just a great honor to welcome him in Brussels for the first time ever.

 ( Comic con brussels is your celebration of geek culture in the heart of europe!

You will find us at the beautiful Tour & Taxis site near the Brussels North train station. At Comic Con Brussels you will find Dealers, Artists, Actors, ... It's a Con that brings together all the things you love:
Comics, cosplay, gaming, films, manga, collectibles, anime, tv series, clothing, toys, gadgets and lots more!!!

There are still tickets at the register - Cosplay ticket 25 euro & standard ticket 30 euro )

description:
Author : @Kiri Karma
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Christopher Lloyd

Christopher Lloyd

aka 'Doc'/dr. Emmett Brown, Uncle Fester, Dr. Doom, Kruge,..
Back To The Future Trilogy - The Addams Family - Who Framed Roger Rabbit - Star Trek - ...

Great Scott!
Our next guest has had such an impact on pop culture that we can speak of a living legend and icon.
Since the 1960s, he has made people smile, laugh and dream.

From a Taxi to a flying Delorean and beyond the boundaries of time and space.

It's a real honor to welcome the most famous time-traveller in the mulitverse and it's his only European show this year!

The one and only Christopher Lloyd is coming to celebrate his 84th birthday at the convention for all the real fans: Comic Con Brussels!

Christopher was in all the Back To The Future movies as 'Doc', Uncle Fester in The Addams Family, Dr. Doom in Who Framed Roger Rabbit, Kruge in Star Trek, Clue and significant roles in 12 Monkeys, Cyberchase, Anastasia, One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest, Piranha 3D and 3DD, The Pagemaster, The Simpsons, Rick and Morty and in the future even in the new season of The Mandalorian..

It's just a great honor to welcome him in Brussels for the first time ever.

 ( Comic con brussels is your celebration of geek culture in the heart of europe!

You will find us at the beautiful Tour & Taxis site near the Brussels North train station. At Comic Con Brussels you will find Dealers, Artists, Actors, ... It's a Con that brings together all the things you love:
Comics, cosplay, gaming, films, manga, collectibles, anime, tv series, clothing, toys, gadgets and lots more!!!

There are still tickets at the register - Cosplay ticket 25 euro & standard ticket 30 euro )

description:
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Jessie Cave

Jessie Cave

aka Lavender Brown
Harry Potter - Black Mirror - Father Brown - ...

Our next guest is most famous as the first love interest of Ron Weasley in the Harry Potter franchise. We are of course talking about Jessie Cave aka Lavender Brown! She was a member of Dumbledore's Army and was Ron's first girlfriend. To make Hermione jealous, Ron would take any chance he could to be with Lavender.

In the movies, she has quite an incredible death scene as during the Battle of Hogwarts she gets attacked by Fenrir Greyback. Jessie Cave went on to appear in Black Mirror, Father Brown and also has a podcast on Youtube.

description:
Comiccon Brussels 2022 - Autumn - Q&A Jessie Cave

Jessie Cave

aka Lavender Brown
Harry Potter - Black Mirror - Father Brown - ...

Our next guest is most famous as the first love interest of Ron Weasley in the Harry Potter franchise. We are of course talking about Jessie Cave aka Lavender Brown! She was a member of Dumbledore's Army and was Ron's first girlfriend. To make Hermione jealous, Ron would take any chance he could to be with Lavender.

In the movies, she has quite an incredible death scene as during the Battle of Hogwarts she gets attacked by Fenrir Greyback. Jessie Cave went on to appear in Black Mirror, Father Brown and also has a podcast on Youtube.

description:
In this picture of downtown Pittsburgh, PA, nine bridges are visible.

At the point, is the confluence of the Monongahela and Allegheny Rivers.  The two rivers form the Ohio River.

To the right, over the Monongahela River are two bridges.  The closest is the Fort Pitt Bridge built in 1959.  It is a steel double-decker bowstring bridge that carries I-376.

To the left, over the Allegheny River, are seven bridges.  The closest is the Fort Duquesne Bridge built in 1969.  The steel tied arch bridge carries I-279.

The photo was taken while we rode the Duquesne Incline.  The photo was taken in May 1997.

description:
c/n 95276
Built in 1967 and flew with the British test registration G-27-41 before being delivered to the Royal Saudi Air Force with the serial 53-671, later changed to 203. She returned to the UK in January 1986 using the British military serial ZF579 and was stored with British Aerospace at Warton along with other ex-Saudi Lightnings waiting for a potential resale. Sadly, no deal was forthcoming and instead the aircraft were disposed of to various museums, collections and private individuals.
ZF579 arrived here in April 2000 and is maintained in full ground-running condition, wearing her genuine Saudi colours.
Gatwick Aviation Museum
Charlwood, Surrey, UK
30th April 2022

description:
El poblado talayótico de Torre d'en Galmés, situado en Menorca, es uno de los yacimientos arqueológicos más grandes de las Islas Baleares. Está situado sobre una colina desde la cual se observa gran parte del sur de la isla.
Cronológicamente, perduró desde la época pretalayótica (antes del 1400 a.C) hasta la época romana. No obstante, la mayoría de las estructuras visibles en la actualidad corresponden a la edad del Hierro.

Ofrece monumentalidad y variedad de restos: tres talayotes, un sistema de recogida de aguas pluviales, tres salas hipóstilas, un recinto de taula, 27 viviendas documentadas y diversas cuevas excavadas en la roca.

El poblado está dominado por tres talayotes, que ocupan la parte más alta como corresponde a su función de atalayas de vigilancia y control del territorio. Muy cerca de los talayotes se encuentra un espacio de carácter religioso llamado recinto de taula. Por todo el poblado se pueden observar edificaciones circulares destinadas a la vida doméstica, algunas de ellas excavadas y restauradas durante las últimas décadas.

En la parte baja de la colina se encuentran algunas viviendas con sala hipóstila, o sala con columnas, estructura adosada que servía como almacén o habitación auxiliar. Otra característica a destacar del poblado talayótico es el medio de aprovechamiento del agua de lluvia, mediante filtros naturales excavados en la roca y canalizaciones que la conducían hasta grandes depósitos.

Por lo que respecta a los materiales arqueológicos recuperados en este yacimiento, destaca una figurita de bronce del dios egipcio Imhotep, encontrada en el recinto de taula. Se trata de la única figura de estas características encontrada en contexto arqueológico, fuera de Egipto.

description:
We visited the Dutch-Caribbean Island of Bonaire in 2015.  During our shore excursion of the island, we saw several donkeys along the road.

Donkeys have been living on Bonaire for hundreds of years.  They were brought over by the  Spanish for manual labor in the salt trade.  They were released and set free when technology improved.  Hundreds now roam the island.

description: By Erica Rossetti

The Edward C. Allworth Veterans’ Home in Lebanon, Oregon, is named for OSU alumnus Maj. Edward Christopher Allworth, who received the Congressional Medal of Honor in World War I for leading a canal crossing that led to the capture of 100 enemy troops during the Meuse-Argonne Battle.

Allworth graduated from Oregon Agricultural College, as OSU was then known, in 1916. In 1925 he became the first director of the Memorial Union, a position he held until his retirement in 1963.

description: O Palácio Real de Queluz, também chamado de Palácio Nacional de Queluz, consiste num palácio do século XVIII. Um dos últimos grandes edifícios em estilo rococó erguidos na Europa, o imóvel foi construído como um recanto de verão para D. Pedro de Bragança. Serviu como um discreto lugar de encarceramento para a rainha D. Maria I, enquanto demente e sobretudo despois da morte de D. Pedro, em 1786. Após o incêndio que atingiu o Palácio da Ajuda em 1794, o Palácio de Queluz tornou-se a residência oficial do Príncipe Regente português, o futuro D. João VI e de sua família. Permaneceu assim até à fuga da Família Real para o Brasil, em 1807, devido às Invasões Francesas. A construção do Palácio iniciou-se em 1747, tendo como arquitecto Mateus Vicente de Oliveira. Apesar de ser muito menor, é chamado frequentemente o "Versailles português". A partir de 1826, o palácio deixou lentamente de ser o eleito pelos soberanos portugueses. Após um grave incêndio ocorrido em 1934, o qual destruiu o seu interior, o monumento foi extensivamente restaurado e, hoje, encontra-se aberto ao público. Uma das alas do Palácio de Queluz, o Pavilhão de Dona Maria, construído entre 1785 e 1792 pelo arquitecto Manuel Caetano de Sousa, é, na actualidade, um quarto de hóspedes exclusivo para chefes de Estado estrangeiros em visita a Portugal. Está classificado como Monumento Nacional desde 1910. www.sintraromantica.net/monumentos/35-palacio-nacional-de...

description: Lake Waccamaw State Park is a North Carolina state park in Columbus County, North Carolina, in the United States. Located near the town of Lake Waccamaw, North Carolina, it covers 2,398-acre (9.70 km2),[3] along the shores of Lake Waccamaw, a Carolina bay. Recent work by the U.S. Geological Survey has interpreted the Carolina Bays as relict thermokarst lakes that formed several thousands of years ago when the climate was colder, drier, and windier.[4] Thermokarst lakes develop by thawing of frozen ground (permafrost) and by subsequent modification by wind and water. Thus, this interpretation suggests that permafrost once extended as far south as the Carolina Bays during the last ice age and (or) previous ice ages.

Divers 2022 - Toutankhamon

Une Fantastique Exposition Immersive
L'exposition Toutankhamon : Sa Tombe et Ses Tresors offre une plongee inedite dans l'Egypte Antique. Avec ses centaines d'objets parfaitement reconstitues, ses decors epoustouflants et ses explications passionnantes, c'est l'expo la plus complete au monde pour decouvrir la vie du jeune roi. Pret(e)s a voyager dans la legende des pharaons ?
1922 - 2022 : 100 ans depuis la decouverte du tombeau du celebre pharaon
4 novembre 1922, Louxor. Apres cinq annees de fouilles infructueuses dans la Vallee des Rois, l'archeologue britannique Howard Carter fait une decouverte incroyable, qui reste a ce jour, sans precedent ! Eclaire par la lueur de sa bougie, il decouvre l'impressionnante tombe doree du pharaon Toutankhamon, mort il y a plus de 3000 ans, entoure de tous ses tresors.

Toutankhamon - Pharaon D'une Dynastie
Toutankhamon monta sur le trone en 1332 av. J.-C. a l'age de 9 ans en tant que l'un des derniers rois de la XVIIIe dynastie. Son pere etait le roi heretique Akhenaton. La realisation la plus importante de son regne fut le rejet des reformes religieuses radicales de son pere, qui avaient destabilise tout le pays. Selon les dernieres etudes, le jeune roi souffrait de graves maladies. Toutankhamon est decede apres neuf ans sur le trone et sa mort reste un mystere a ce jour.

Son tombeau et ses tresors : plus de 1000 objets a decouvrir
Le Metropolitan Museum a envoye Harry Burton comme photographe des fouilles - il etait ' l'oeil et la memoire de Carter '. Avec son enorme appareil photo et ses plaques negatives encombrantes, il arpentait inlassablement le lieu de la decouverte, son laboratoire (qu'il avait installe dans la tombe de Sethos II), et sa chambre noire improvisee dans la tombe voisine KV 55. Chaque etape des travaux d'excavation a ete documentee en photographies, jusque dans les moindres details. En tout, 2 800 negatifs sur verre grand format ont ete tires, et repertorient toutes les decouvertes et leur emplacement dans la tombe.
La gigantesque exposition Toutankhamon abrite plus de 1 000 pieces et une impressionnante abondance artistique de l'Egypte ancienne. Decouvrez vite ses tresors !

Replacing an earlier scanned photo with a better version 31-Mar-17 + DeNoise AI 06-Oct-22.

This aircraft was operated by Sterling European Airways of behalf of Israir until 30-Sep-01 but still carried Israir titles.  It visited Manchester again the following week with Sterling titles (see photo OY-SEH 3).

First flown with the Boeing test registration N1787B, this aircraft was delivered to Itochu Airlease and leased to Sterling European Airways as OY-SEH in Jan-99.

It was sub-leased to Transavia Holland between Apr/Sep-99 and to Air Berlin from Apr/Jun-01.  The aircraft was sub-leased to Israir (Israel) between Jul/Sep-01.  It was returned to the lessor in Mar-07 and was due to be leased to Transavia Holland as PH-HSW.

Instead, it was leased to Transavia France as F-GZHV in May-07 and was fitted with blended winglets before it entered service.

The aircraft was temporarily stored at Nantes, France in Mar-20 due to the COVID-19 Pandemic and returned to service in Jul-20.  It was stored at Perpignan, France in Sep-22 (it's nearly 24 years old so I'm not sure if it's permanently retired).  Updated 06-Oct-22.

description:
Launch Floral Nectar for Honeys

De afgelopen twee jaar werkten wij, founder van De Peerdegaerdt Hèlen Sturm, vegan chef Maartje Borst, herborist Lisette Kreischer en ondernemer Joost Verbakel aan 'de geboorte’ van onze mooie Floral Nectar. Een goudkleurig brouwsel gemaakt in co-creatie met de natuur, geïnspireerd door de seizoenen en in dienst van de Aarde en haar bestuivers.

Tijdens een heerlijke, zonnige september dag vond de zoete lancering plaats van dit bijzondere nieuwe product – Floral Nectar for Honeys . Op een magische plek in Nederland, het hart van The Happiest Healthy Farm, namen wij een select gezelschap op interactieve wijze mee in de totstandkoming van ons honingachtige, goudkleurige brouwsel.

Omringd door een ontluikende herfst hebben we in de eeuwenoude fruitboomgaard appels en peren geplukt, geproefd van het hand geperste sapje,  een meanderende kruidenwandeling heeft Lisette geheimen onthuld over de medicinale werking van kruiden en planten om vervolgens na een verrassende tasting door Maartje verwend te worden met plantaardige seizoenslekkernijen. Dit alles ondersteund door de fenomenale bestuivende verhalen van Joost van Stichting The Pollinators.

We zijn trots op de enthousiaste reacties over ons nieuwe gouden brouwsel: een kruidige en zoete nectar, niet afgenomen van, maar in samenwerking met de bijen. En in diverse smaken, want Moeder Natuur is briljant; ze brengt ons allerlei bijzondere ingrediënten in een seizoensgebonden jasje, iets waar wij ons met plezier door hebben laten inspireren.

Vol vertrouwen kijken we uit naar een kennismaking met een breder publiek met behulp van onze eerste ambassadeurs.

description: Ecuador, 04 de octubre de 2022.- El estudio de la ciudadanía y de los valores éticos y cívicos, obligatorio en todas las unidades educativas, es la manera más acertada para el combate a la corrupción, manifestó la asambleísta Yeseña Guamaní, al presentar ante diversos actores del sector educativo el proyecto de reformas a la Ley de Educación Intercultural. La legisladora, en su proyecto, destaca que tener leyes estrictas anticorrupción no garantiza que haya una aplicación efectiva; si hay leyes estrictas sin una educación que anteponga valores, la corrupción seguirá floreciendo, por lo que es crucial dedicar prioridad y atención a la educación. Foto Cortesia  / Asamblea Nacional

description: Church of All Saints, North Cerney, Gloucestershire, 22 September 2022. Core is 12th Century Norman but 15th Century fire caused much damage, including the nave roof and upper stage of tower so the church was virtualy rebuilt. It was again restored in late 19th Century by Waller. Pictured is a very unusual squint passage between the south chapel and the chancel. Adjacent is a Tudor-arched entrance to stairs to the rood loft.

description:
August - Divers 2022

Tapis de Fleurs 2022 Cet evenement a deja eu lieu  Du 12 au 15 aout 2022 sur la Grand-Place de Bruxelles (construction du tapis de fleurs le vendredi 12 aout).  Tous les 2 ans, pendant l'ete, un tapis de fleurs de begonias de 77 m x 24 m prend ses quartiers sur la Grand-Place. A chaque edition, une creation specifique est realisee.  Pour reproduire les motifs, le dessin grandeur nature sera reporte sur une feuille plastique transparente et micro-perforee. Le tapis est ensuite realise par pres de 120 volontaires qui installent pres d'un million de begonias (a raison de 300 par m2). Le tout, en moins de 4 heures. Modele du Tapis de Fleurs de 1971  Pour marquer ses 50 ans et sa 22e edition, le Tapis de Fleurs 2022 fait un clin d'oeil au premier visuel de 1971. Tous les elements presents dans le premier modele de 1971 figurent dans le modele 2022, y compris l'archange Saint-Michel et le Lion belge.

description:
Pictured: Mr Kevin Baaron posing a question to the panel.

The 2022 Atlantic Future Forum (AFF) will take place on board HMS Queen Elizabeth, Wednesday 28th September at anchor off New York City during her deployment to the USA.

The event, two day conference, brings together the brightest minds and most influential thinkers-from defence and beyond-to strengthen the US-UK special relationship and encourage collaboration between the public and private sector. Through a series of keynote speeches and panel discussions, the Forum will explore how both private and public sector and US and UK interests can work together to maximise the opportunities – and mitigate the risks – posed by current and future technologies.

The Forum will be an opportunity for senior politicians, policymakers, military leaders and academia, together with business leaders and entrepreneurs to discuss the new dimensions of international security and the future technologies which will define the next decade and beyond.

The Forum will be led by the Department for International Trade (DIT), working alongside the Ministry of Defence (MOD) and Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office (FCDO) to strengthen the trade and economic pillars of the Euro-Atlantic alliance and reinforce our security and defence partnerships with like-minded, democratic allies. The AFF is chaired by Lord Sedwill and will be co-hosted by the First Sea Lord, Admiral Sir Ben Key and HM Ambassador Dame Karen Pierce.

HMS Queen Elizabeth sailed from Portsmouth on the 7th September 2022 for New York, United States of America, to host Atlantic Future Forum before continuing on operations.

description:
El presidente de la Junta de Andalucía, Juanma Moreno, se ha reunido
esta tarde en el Palacio de San Telmo con la directora general de la
Asociación Nuevo Hogar Betania, Begoña Arana Álvarez.

Esta Asociación sin ánimo de lucro fue fundada para atender a cualquier
persona que se encuentre en situación de exclusión social, así como para
dar soluciones a la pobreza, al hambre y apoyar proyectos que mejoren la
salud y el bienestar.

El compromiso del Gobierno andaluz para ayudar a las personas más
vulnerables es firme y rotundo, tal como lo demuestran algunas de las
medidas que se han adoptado como el Plan de Refuerzo Alimentarios para
18.000 estudiantes en situación de vulnerabilidad, la tarjeta monedero
de la Cruz Roja, el comedor escolar que atiende a 210.000 usuarios
diarios de los que el 45% tiene gratuidad total y el 70% cuenta con
alguna bonificación y la gratuidad total para el 40% de los usuarios de
todos los servicios complementarios.

También cabe recordar la ampliación del Programa extraordinario de
alojamiento e inserción social a personas sin hogar a través de atención
ambulatoria y residencial puesto en marcha a través de la Red Andaluza
de Lucha contra la Pobreza y la Exclusión Social, que forma parte de un
amplio paquete de medidas desplegado desde la Junta para dar respuesta
inmediata a necesidades urgentes y que se sustenta en la atención a las
personas sin hogar en centros de todas las provincias.

Además, existen otras iniciativas como la de promover un proyecto de Ley que adapte la Renta Mínima de Inclusión Social andaluza para
complementarla con el Ingreso Mínimo Vital, los trabajos para aprobar
una Ley de Familias en Andalucía o la Estrategia Regional Andaluza para
la Cohesión e Inclusión Social en Zonas Desfavorecidas que se
desarrollará en más de 90 barrios para promover la inserción social y
combatir el absentismo escolar en familias vulnerables.

description:
HMS QUEEN ELIZABETH HOSTS ATLANTIC FUTURE FORUM CONFERENCE

On 28-29 September the 5th Atlantic Future Forum (AFF22) was held on board Royal Navy Flagship HMS Queen Elizabeth, anchored off New York. Delegates from across the political, military and business spheres were formally welcomed by Captain Ian Feasey, Commanding Officer. Over the course of the two days panel discussions will be held and delegates will have the opportunity to talk with industry partnters.

The Forum will be led by the Department for International Trade (DIT), working alongside the Ministry of Defence (MOD) and Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office (FCDO) to strengthen the trade and economic pillars of the Euro-Atlantic alliance and reinforce our security and defence partnerships with like-minded, democratic allies. The AFF is chaired by Lord Sedwill and will be co-hosted by the First Sea Lord, Admiral Sir Ben Key and HM Ambassador Dame Karen Pierce.

HMS Queen Elizabeth is the lead ship of the Queen Elizabeth class of aircraft carriers and the Fleet Flagship of the Royal Navy. She is named in honour of the first HMS Queen Elizabeth, a World War I era super-dreadnought, which in turn was named after Queen Elizabeth I. The ship carries her namesake ship's honours, as well as her Tudor rose-adorned crest and motto.

description:
Author : @Kiri Karma
Divers 2022 - Toutankhamon

Une Fantastique Exposition Immersive
L'exposition Toutankhamon : Sa Tombe et Ses Tresors offre une plongee inedite dans l'Egypte Antique. Avec ses centaines d'objets parfaitement reconstitues, ses decors epoustouflants et ses explications passionnantes, c'est l'expo la plus complete au monde pour decouvrir la vie du jeune roi. Pret(e)s a voyager dans la legende des pharaons ?
1922 - 2022 : 100 ans depuis la decouverte du tombeau du celebre pharaon
4 novembre 1922, Louxor. Apres cinq annees de fouilles infructueuses dans la Vallee des Rois, l'archeologue britannique Howard Carter fait une decouverte incroyable, qui reste a ce jour, sans precedent ! Eclaire par la lueur de sa bougie, il decouvre l'impressionnante tombe doree du pharaon Toutankhamon, mort il y a plus de 3000 ans, entoure de tous ses tresors.

Toutankhamon - Pharaon D'une Dynastie
Toutankhamon monta sur le trone en 1332 av. J.-C. a l'age de 9 ans en tant que l'un des derniers rois de la XVIIIe dynastie. Son pere etait le roi heretique Akhenaton. La realisation la plus importante de son regne fut le rejet des reformes religieuses radicales de son pere, qui avaient destabilise tout le pays. Selon les dernieres etudes, le jeune roi souffrait de graves maladies. Toutankhamon est decede apres neuf ans sur le trone et sa mort reste un mystere a ce jour.

Son tombeau et ses tresors : plus de 1000 objets a decouvrir
Le Metropolitan Museum a envoye Harry Burton comme photographe des fouilles - il etait ' l'oeil et la memoire de Carter '. Avec son enorme appareil photo et ses plaques negatives encombrantes, il arpentait inlassablement le lieu de la decouverte, son laboratoire (qu'il avait installe dans la tombe de Sethos II), et sa chambre noire improvisee dans la tombe voisine KV 55. Chaque etape des travaux d'excavation a ete documentee en photographies, jusque dans les moindres details. En tout, 2 800 negatifs sur verre grand format ont ete tires, et repertorient toutes les decouvertes et leur emplacement dans la tombe.
La gigantesque exposition Toutankhamon abrite plus de 1 000 pieces et une impressionnante abondance artistique de l'Egypte ancienne. Decouvrez vite ses tresors !

description:
c/n unknown
Built in 1956 as a Hunter F.6 for the Royal Air Force with the serial XG226. Served with 66 and 92 Squadrons, then 229 Operational Conversion Unit (229OCU) before being converted to a Hunter F.6A and flying from RAF Brawdy with Nos.1 & 2 Tactical Weapons Units.
She was retired to the Fire School at Catterick in February 1983 and allocated the maintenance serial 8800M.
She was disposed of as a complete airframe, but parts are now spread across the UK with the centre fuselage section forming part of the recreated Hunter FR.10 [BAPC548] at the East Midlands Aeropark.
The nose section arrived here in January 2003 and has been painted in genuine ‘Blue Diamonds’ colours from her time with 92 Squadron.
RAF Manston History Museum
Manston, Kent, UK
30th April 2022

description:
August - Divers 2022

Tapis de Fleurs 2022 Cet evenement a deja eu lieu  Du 12 au 15 aout 2022 sur la Grand-Place de Bruxelles (construction du tapis de fleurs le vendredi 12 aout).  Tous les 2 ans, pendant l'ete, un tapis de fleurs de begonias de 77 m x 24 m prend ses quartiers sur la Grand-Place. A chaque edition, une creation specifique est realisee.  Pour reproduire les motifs, le dessin grandeur nature sera reporte sur une feuille plastique transparente et micro-perforee. Le tapis est ensuite realise par pres de 120 volontaires qui installent pres d'un million de begonias (a raison de 300 par m2). Le tout, en moins de 4 heures. Modele du Tapis de Fleurs de 1971  Pour marquer ses 50 ans et sa 22e edition, le Tapis de Fleurs 2022 fait un clin d'oeil au premier visuel de 1971. Tous les elements presents dans le premier modele de 1971 figurent dans le modele 2022, y compris l'archange Saint-Michel et le Lion belge.

description:
Author : @Kiri Karma
Divers 2022 - Toutankhamon

Une Fantastique Exposition Immersive
L'exposition Toutankhamon : Sa Tombe et Ses Tresors offre une plongee inedite dans l'Egypte Antique. Avec ses centaines d'objets parfaitement reconstitues, ses decors epoustouflants et ses explications passionnantes, c'est l'expo la plus complete au monde pour decouvrir la vie du jeune roi. Pret(e)s a voyager dans la legende des pharaons ?
1922 - 2022 : 100 ans depuis la decouverte du tombeau du celebre pharaon
4 novembre 1922, Louxor. Apres cinq annees de fouilles infructueuses dans la Vallee des Rois, l'archeologue britannique Howard Carter fait une decouverte incroyable, qui reste a ce jour, sans precedent ! Eclaire par la lueur de sa bougie, il decouvre l'impressionnante tombe doree du pharaon Toutankhamon, mort il y a plus de 3000 ans, entoure de tous ses tresors.

Toutankhamon - Pharaon D'une Dynastie
Toutankhamon monta sur le trone en 1332 av. J.-C. a l'age de 9 ans en tant que l'un des derniers rois de la XVIIIe dynastie. Son pere etait le roi heretique Akhenaton. La realisation la plus importante de son regne fut le rejet des reformes religieuses radicales de son pere, qui avaient destabilise tout le pays. Selon les dernieres etudes, le jeune roi souffrait de graves maladies. Toutankhamon est decede apres neuf ans sur le trone et sa mort reste un mystere a ce jour.

Son tombeau et ses tresors : plus de 1000 objets a decouvrir
Le Metropolitan Museum a envoye Harry Burton comme photographe des fouilles - il etait ' l'oeil et la memoire de Carter '. Avec son enorme appareil photo et ses plaques negatives encombrantes, il arpentait inlassablement le lieu de la decouverte, son laboratoire (qu'il avait installe dans la tombe de Sethos II), et sa chambre noire improvisee dans la tombe voisine KV 55. Chaque etape des travaux d'excavation a ete documentee en photographies, jusque dans les moindres details. En tout, 2 800 negatifs sur verre grand format ont ete tires, et repertorient toutes les decouvertes et leur emplacement dans la tombe.
La gigantesque exposition Toutankhamon abrite plus de 1 000 pieces et une impressionnante abondance artistique de l'Egypte ancienne. Decouvrez vite ses tresors !

Thousands of people gathered around the British parliament on Saturday 8 October 1922 to form the first ever human chain to surround the building to protest against Julian Assange's continued imprisonment and extradition. Many of the activists had travelled hundreds of miles - I met people who had travelled from Belgium, France and Germany. The long line of people snaked around parliament's perimeter railings and across both Lambeth and Westminster bridges as well as traversing the south side of the river between St. Thomas' Hospital and Lambeth Palace, each person holding the hand of the person next to them. As a few people attached yellow ribbons to the railings by parliament they were immediately instructed by the police to remove them. For the last eight months Julian Assange, who is being held in the maximum security Belmarsh Prison, has been kept completely isolated and without visitors, except for his lawyers. He been detained in appalling conditions and the former UN Special Rapporteur on torture, Neils Melzer, commented in 2019 that Assange showed 'all the symptoms typical for prolonged exposure to psychological torture,' adding that 'what we have seen from the UK Government is outright contempt for Mr Assange's rights and integrity.' www.ohchr.org/en/press-releases/2019/11/un-expert-torture... The United States wants to extradite Julian Assange to the United States on a supposed charge of espionage. However, Assange's real crime is that he revealed US and Western war crimes in Afghanistan, Iraq and elsewhere. As the founder and chief editor of Wikileaks he has provoked Washington's fury by the publication of US Army intelligence files leaked by Chelsea Manning in 2010 as well as subsequent revelations which have embarrassed the American establishment, including Democratic Party emails which showed how senior officials in the party's national committee favoured Hilary Clinton over the more progressive and radical Bernie Sanders. Former Home Secretary Priti Patel signed off on the extradition request earlier in the year, but that order is currently being appealed by Assange's lawyers, who are awaiting a decision by the High Court on whether they will agree to hear it. As far as I understand it, the remit of the appeal has been restricted to examining the United States' claimed legal promises on how Assange will be treated, rather than to the wider issues of freedom of speech, the CIA plot to assassinate him, the extent to which the evidence against him has obviously been fabricated or as to whether his treatment in Belmarsh Prison has amounted to torture. The former Labour Party leader, Jeremy Corbyn, attended Saturday's protest, as did the former leader of Unite, Len McLuskey, the independent (former Labour Party MP) Claudia Webbe, the comedian and actor Russel Brand and Mr Assange's wife, Stella. According to the Morning Star and the Evening Standard, Corbyn said "I would say to MPs of any party, you're there to represent democracy and rights. That's what you sign up for. If Julian Assange is extradited, it will set forth fear among other journalists of doing anything to expose the truth. It becomes self-censorship of journalists all around the world. They'll say, 'hang, on, I'm not touching that, look what happened to Julian Assange.'" morningstaronline.co.uk/article/b/thousands-gather-human-... www.standard.co.uk/news/london/russell-brand-julian-assan... If Assange is convicted in the United States on the charges of espionage for exposing US war crimes in Afghanistan and Iraq as well as other wrongdoing by the United States and other governments, he faces up to 175 years in prison. Two days after the protest, it was reported that Assange had contracted covid.

Ivo Cré, Director Policy and Projects, POLIS

BCWF Wrestling - La Rentree Des Clashs 2022 - Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Vs Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Eddie Dark & Tibo Hendrik & Legion Von Creed Def. (Pin) Ymah Pain & Jason TNK & 'The Abanoub' Mayeck, Rocky Jones

Info on the match : Avant de commencer le match, le GM avait encore plus de ' Encore une chose ' dans sa manche. Non seulement il a autorise l'annonceur Rocky Jones dans le match, mais dans une grande surprise, il a egalement presente le monstre hollandais, Ymah Pain !
Voordat de wedstrijd begon, had de GM nog wat 'One more things' in petto. Niet alleen liet hij omroeper Rocky Jones toe in de wedstrijd, maar als grote verrassing introduceerde hij ook het monster uit Nederland, Ymah Pain!
Before starting the match, the GM had some more 'One more things' up his sleeve. Not only did he allow announcer Rocky Jones into the match, but in a big surprise he introduced the monster from Holland, Ymah Pain, as well!

Avec toutes les chances contre eux, Eddie et Tibo ont demande a Joey de reintegrer Mama, s'ils remportaient la victoire improbable. Joey a accepte, mais son rire s'est vite transforme en panique quand Eddie a sorti son troisieme partenaire pour le match, LEGION !
Met hun rug tegen de muur, vroegen Eddie en Tibo Joey om Mama weer aan te nemen, mochten ze de onwaarschijnlijke overwinning behalen. Joey stemde toe, maar zijn lach sloeg al snel om in paniek toen Eddie zijn derde partner voor de wedstrijd tevoorschijn haalde, LEGION!
With the odds stacked against them, Eddie and Tibo asked Joey to reinstate Mama, should they pick up the unlikely win. Joey agreed, but his laughter soon turned to panic as Eddie brought out his third partner for the match, LEGION!

A la fin, Eddie a reussi a remporter la victoire inattendue sur Mayeck. Il a termine la soiree en annoncant que Mama serait de retour au prochain spectacle !
Na een heen en weer wedstrijd wist Eddie dan toch de overwinning te pakken door Mayeck te pinnen. Hij eindigde de avond door aan te kondigen dat Mama terug zou keren bij de volgende show!
After a back-and forth match, Eddie managed to pick up the upset win by pinning Mayeck. He ended the night by announcing Mama would be back at the next show!

 ( Il sera bientot temps de retourner a l'ecole ! Mais cela ne signifie pas que vous ne pouvez pas passer un bon moment chez nous. Venez rejoindre le BWS le 2 septembre a Grivegnee pour une nuit de catch ! Retournons a l'ecole en beaute. )

description:
BCWF Wrestling - La Rentree Des Clashs 2022 - Alex Curly & Eddie Dark Vs Joe Destroy & Yo

Alex Curly & Eddie Dark (The Belgian Dream) Def. (Pin) Joe Destroy & Yo (Farmers From Hell)

Info on the match : Avant le debut du match, le directeur general a annonce que si la Dream Team gagnait en moins de 5 minutes, elle obtiendrait une chance pour le titre. Alors qu'ils ont a peine reussi a le faire, Joey a declare que ce ne serait jamais un titre par equipe, mais un simple contre ZAG pour le titre europeen !
Voordat de wedstrijd begon, kondigde de GM aan dat als Dream Team binnen 5 minuten zou winnen, ze een titel zouden krijgen. Toen ze daar op de valreep in slaagden, zei Joey dat het geen kans op de tag team titles zou zijn, maar een singles match voor ZAG's European title!
Before the match started, the GM announced that if Dream Team win in under 5 minutes, they would get a title shot. When they just barely managed to do so, Joey said that it was never going to be a tag team title shot, but a singles one for ZAG's European title!

Eddie a decide de donner le coup a son partenaire, affirmant qu'Alex est la nouvelle generation et l'avenir de l'entreprise.
Eddie besloot zijn partner de kans te geven en zei dat Alex de nieuwe generatie en toekomst van BCWF is.
Eddie decided to give the shot to his partner, saying that Alex is the new generation and future of the company.

Announcer : Rocky Jones
joey D

 ( Il sera bientot temps de retourner a l'ecole ! Mais cela ne signifie pas que vous ne pouvez pas passer un bon moment chez nous. Venez rejoindre le BWS le 2 septembre a Grivegnee pour une nuit de catch ! Retournons a l'ecole en beaute. )

5. Segundo debate del Proyecto de Ley Orgánica de Transparencia y Acceso a la Información Pública.

The fog bell that was used to warn ships on a foggy day.

n 1857, work began on the present tower. The lower half of the twenty-four-foot-tall, cylindrical tower was built of granite, and the upper half of brick. The lantern was made of cast iron and housed a fifth-order Fresnel lens showing a fixed white light.

The lighthouse was featured in the movie Forest Gump featuring Tom Hanks, concluded his cross-country run on the runway of Marshall Point Lighthouse.

description:
El presidente de la Junta de Andalucía, Juanma Moreno, ha anunciado que a partir del año que viene la vacuna frente al papiloma formará parte del calendario vacunal de los varones a partir de los doce años con el objetivo de prevenir las enfermedades que produce también en
ellos este virus.


Moreno ha explicado que los más de 47.000 residentes en Andalucía varones que nacieron en el año 2011 se podrán vacunar al igual que ya lo hacen las chicas, lo que supone un ahorropara las familias andaluzas de 345 euros por cada niño vacunado. Esta nueva incorporación al calendario vacunal se suma a las ya incluidas en los últimos tres
años y es que ha concretado que desde el 2020 se han incorporado la vacuna de la meningitis ACWY a los doce meses y en adolescentes de 12 a 18 años, la de la meningitis B en lactantes y la de la gripe en niños de 6 meses a 4 años y 11 meses para esta campaña 2022-23. “Hoy,
Andalucía es la comunidad autónoma con uno de los calendarios más completos de toda Europa”.


Además, ha recordado que hoy lunes ha empezado por primera vez la campaña de vacunación contra la gripe a los niños de entre 6 y 59 meses en Andalucía, así como para los mayores de 65 años. A este respecto, ha indicado que debemos ser conscientes de que entre 60 y 80 años hay casos graves con necesidad de ingresos hospitalarios y que la población
infantil es el grupo donde más incidencia hay, a lo que se suma que los niños tienen un papel destacado en la transmisión del virus al resto de la población.


Inauguración de la rehabilitación integral del Antiguo Hospital de Andújar
El presidente andaluz ha asistido a la inauguración de la rehabilitación integral del Antiguo Hospital de Andújar, un compromiso del Gobierno andaluz que se ha hecho una realidad y que ya está listo para dar servicio sanitario de calidad en Urgencias, Atención Primaria y
algunas especialidades y con nuevos servicios que no había hasta el momento.


Así, este Hospital del Siglo XVII, declarado Bien de Interés Cultural, ha pasado a convertirse en un centro de salud moderno y completamente reformado, algo que se ha conseguido con la colaboración de las distintas administraciones, ya que se trata de un edificio cedido por el
Ayuntamiento y totalmente reformado con un proyecto decidido, ejecutado y financiado por laJunta de Andalucía, aunque Moreno ha apostillado que “el tesón de los vecinos de Andújar ha sido una pieza clave”. En este punto, ha incidido en que la filosofía del Gobierno andaluz en materia de infraestructuras ha sido la de mejorar y ampliar la red de infraestructuras sanitarias, recuperando edificios y modernizando los servicios. A este respecto, ha mencionado algunos ejemplos como el Hospital Alto Guadalquivir con casi 9 millones de euros en inversiones para dar mejor respuesta sanitaria en Andújar y en otros
siete municipios.

Para concluir, ha señalado que, en toda la provincia de Jaén, solo durante 2022, se están llevando a cabo reformas en centros sanitarios de cuarenta municipios, a la vez que ha subrayado que, en los últimos cuatro años, la inversión total en obras y equipamientos ha ascendido a los 44 millones de euros.

Moreno ha estado acompañado por la consejera de Salud y Consumo, Catalina García; el alcalde de Andújar, Pedro Luis Rodríguez, y el delegado del Gobierno de la Junta en Jaén, Jesús Estrella.

años y es que ha concretado que desde el 2020 se han incorporado la vacuna de la meningitis ACWY a los doce meses y en adolescentes de 12 a 18 años, la de la meningitis B en lactantes y la de la gripe en niños de 6 meses a 4 años y 11 meses para esta campaña 2022-23. “Hoy,
Andalucía es la comunidad autónoma con uno de los calendarios más completos de toda Europa”.


Además, ha recordado que hoy lunes ha empezado por primera vez la campaña de vacunación contra la gripe a los niños de entre 6 y 59 meses en Andalucía, así como para los mayores de 65 años. A este respecto, ha indicado que debemos ser conscientes de que entre 60 y 80 años hay casos graves con necesidad de ingresos hospitalarios y que la población
infantil es el grupo donde más incidencia hay, a lo que se suma que los niños tienen un papel destacado en la transmisión del virus al resto de la población.

El presidente andaluz ha asistido a la inauguración de la rehabilitación integral del Antiguo Hospital de Andújar, un compromiso del Gobierno andaluz que se ha hecho una realidad y que ya está listo para dar servicio sanitario de calidad en Urgencias, Atención Primaria y
algunas especialidades y con nuevos servicios que no había hasta el momento.


Así, este Hospital del Siglo XVII, declarado Bien de Interés Cultural, ha pasado a convertirse en un centro de salud moderno y completamente reformado, algo que se ha conseguido con la colaboración de las distintas administraciones, ya que se trata de un edificio cedido por el
Ayuntamiento y totalmente reformado con un proyecto decidido, ejecutado y financiado por laJunta de Andalucía, aunque Moreno ha apostillado que “el tesón de los vecinos de Andújar ha sido una pieza clave”. En este punto, ha incidido en que la filosofía del Gobierno andaluz en materia de infraestructuras ha sido la de mejorar y ampliar la red de infraestructuras sanitarias, recuperando edificios y modernizando los servicios. A este respecto, ha mencionado algunos ejemplos como el Hospital Alto Guadalquivir con casi 9 millones de euros en inversiones para dar mejor respuesta sanitaria en Andújar y en otros
siete municipios.

Para concluir, ha señalado que, en toda la provincia de Jaén, solo durante 2022, se están llevando a cabo reformas en centros sanitarios de cuarenta municipios, a la vez que ha subrayado que, en los últimos cuatro años, la inversión total en obras y equipamientos ha ascendido a los 44 millones de euros.
